      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a superlative intersection of mechanical purity and preservation. Powered by the high-revving S54 straight-six, the engine exhibits perfect compression across all cylinders with a dual-VANOS system that has been meticulously serviced to ensure optimal cam timing. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission offers precise gate entry, paired with a subframe that has been proactively reinforced to maintain structural rigidity under lateral load. The exterior retains its factory luster with no evidence of panel misalignment or clear-coat failure. From the M-Variable limited-slip differential to the crisp throttle response of the individual throttle bodies, every component operates at peak performance parameters, offering a tactile, analog driving experience that is increasingly rare.",
